1
00:00:08,383 --> 00:00:10,177
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Beth] Yay!
- [all laughing]</font>

2
00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:11,678
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, what's that?</font>

3
00:00:11,762 --> 00:00:13,972
<font face="Serif" size="18">Do I hear something
coming down the chimney?</font>

4
00:00:15,974 --> 00:00:19,186
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick Santa-chez here with gifts
from across the multiverse.</font>

5
00:00:19,269 --> 00:00:20,103
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, my God.
- Yes!</font>

6
00:00:20,187 --> 00:00:23,774
<font face="Serif" size="18">For Jerry, an extra dimensional version
of <i>Miracle on 34th Street.</i></font>

7
00:00:23,857 --> 00:00:27,611
<font face="Serif" size="18">Two hours longer!
They fixed my only problem with it!</font>

8
00:00:27,694 --> 00:00:32,074
<font face="Serif" size="18">For Beth, a framed photo of the two of us from
a universe where she wasn't murdered as a child.</font>

9
00:00:32,157 --> 00:00:33,283
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, my God. Dad.</font>

10
00:00:33,367 --> 00:00:37,037
<font face="Serif" size="18">And for Space Beth, the same thing because
we don't know which of you is real.</font>

11
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:38,956
<font face="Serif" size="18">I am also touched.</font>

12
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:40,290
<font face="Serif" size="18">Summer, check your Venmo.</font>

13
00:00:41,250 --> 00:00:44,628
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [gasps] Money? How did you know?!
- You're 17.</font>

14
00:00:44,711 --> 00:00:47,339
<font face="Serif" size="18">And last but not least,
for my number one number two.</font>

15
00:00:47,422 --> 00:00:49,508
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty you asked for this
a long time ago</font>

16
00:00:49,591 --> 00:00:51,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">and I finally went far, far away enough
to get it</font>

17
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:53,595
<font face="Serif" size="18">since shipping would have killed me.</font>

18
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:57,182
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You didn't! No fucking way.
- [all] No fucking way.</font>

19
00:00:57,266 --> 00:01:00,852
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Does it make the noises?
- Of course, that's like half the fun.</font>

20
00:01:00,936 --> 00:01:03,146
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Awesome!
- Whoa, do not turn that on!</font>

21
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:06,441
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't worry. Morty's only going to use
this very honorable weapon</font>

22
00:01:06,525 --> 00:01:09,403
<font face="Serif" size="18">in designated Jedi zones,
like the garage right now.</font>

23
00:01:14,116 --> 00:01:18,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">Holy crap. I hate to say it, but I wish
there was something to attack.</font>

24
00:01:18,203 --> 00:01:20,372
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's too bad nobody bought
a cart of fruit!</font>

25
00:01:20,455 --> 00:01:23,208
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You beautiful son of a bitch.
- Grapefruit!</font>

26
00:01:23,292 --> 00:01:26,253
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mango! Papaya! Watermelon!
A second papaya!</font>

27
00:01:26,336 --> 00:01:28,505
<font face="Serif" size="18">Another watermelon! Strike me down.</font>

28
00:01:28,589 --> 00:01:29,715
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What?
- Strike me down!</font>

29
00:01:29,798 --> 00:01:32,092
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm not striking you down.
- Strike me down.</font>

30
00:01:32,175 --> 00:01:34,386
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'll become a pile of clothes
like that old guy.</font>

31
00:01:34,469 --> 00:01:35,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you'll die, you're drunk.</font>

32
00:01:35,887 --> 00:01:37,598
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Here, I'll do it myself--
- No!</font>

33
00:01:39,766 --> 00:01:42,936
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow, you did it! Just like Obi Wan.
Rick?</font>

34
00:01:43,020 --> 00:01:47,441
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can come out now. I'm serious.
Did you, like, become your clothes?</font>

35
00:01:47,524 --> 00:01:49,026
<font face="Serif" size="18">Are you T-shirt Rick now?</font>

36
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:50,819
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] Psst. Over here, butt fart.</font>

37
00:01:50,902 --> 00:01:52,696
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, that was awesome!
- Right?</font>

38
00:01:52,779 --> 00:01:55,449
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, you know you've been
so great the last couple months.</font>

39
00:01:55,532 --> 00:01:57,868
<font face="Serif" size="18">The family's so happy,
I'm really grateful.</font>

40
00:01:57,951 --> 00:02:00,454
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aw, thanks, kid,
but less talk more melon slaying.</font>

41
00:02:00,537 --> 00:02:01,371
<font face="Serif" size="18">Heads up!</font>

42
00:02:01,455 --> 00:02:02,456
<font face="Serif" size="18">Whoops!</font>

43
00:02:06,627 --> 00:02:08,420
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Shit, open it, Rick!
- Let me do it!</font>

44
00:02:08,503 --> 00:02:10,380
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Get up-- Fucking move!
- Hurry!</font>

45
00:02:10,464 --> 00:02:12,299
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, whoa! Whoa, whoa!</font>

46
00:02:12,382 --> 00:02:15,719
<font face="Serif" size="18">You dropped it perfectly vertical,
Morty. Perfectly fucking vertical!</font>

47
00:02:15,802 --> 00:02:18,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I got it, I got it, aw!
- Oh, shit.</font>

48
00:02:19,556 --> 00:02:21,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Shit.
- Elevator. Elevator.</font>

49
00:02:21,183 --> 00:02:23,101
<font face="Serif" size="18">We gotta get ahead of it.
Level ten?</font>

50
00:02:23,185 --> 00:02:24,394
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, no, no, 15.</font>

51
00:02:25,437 --> 00:02:26,730
<font face="Serif" size="18">[elevator beeping]</font>

52
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:32,069
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, we live over
a cool sushi spot?</font>

53
00:02:32,152 --> 00:02:35,238
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [speaking Japanese]
- <i>Domo. Domo.</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Not now, though.</font>

54
00:02:35,322 --> 00:02:37,741
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, we overshot it.
Good problem to have.</font>

55
00:02:37,824 --> 00:02:40,077
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Still doing the eel roll?
- We should've gone to ten.</font>

56
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,411
<font face="Serif" size="18">No, Morty, not ten.</font>

57
00:02:42,037 --> 00:02:43,955
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Morty, wait, wait.
- Cut it out.</font>

58
00:02:46,083 --> 00:02:46,917
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the fuck?</font>

59
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,755
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Rick?
- You dumb fucking robot.</font>

60
00:02:51,838 --> 00:02:54,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You had one job.
- That job was to be a good grandpa.</font>

61
00:02:54,716 --> 00:02:56,760
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I go where the kid goes.
- Don't touch me.</font>

62
00:02:56,843 --> 00:02:59,471
<font face="Serif" size="18">How long have I--
You said you weren't a robot.</font>

63
00:02:59,554 --> 00:03:00,972
<font face="Serif" size="18">It killed me to lie to you.</font>

64
00:03:01,056 --> 00:03:03,392
<font face="Serif" size="18">But it would have literally
killed me not to lie to you.</font>

65
00:03:03,475 --> 00:03:05,102
<font face="Serif" size="18">Betrayal. Betrayal on all sides.</font>

66
00:03:05,185 --> 00:03:06,228
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't overreact.</font>

67
00:03:06,311 --> 00:03:09,773
<font face="Serif" size="18">I replaced myself towards the beginning
of that whole Knights of the Sun thing.</font>

68
00:03:09,856 --> 00:03:12,901
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm no good to anybody till
I resolve this arch-nemesis crap.</font>

69
00:03:12,984 --> 00:03:14,986
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're hunting the guy
who killed your wife?</font>

70
00:03:15,070 --> 00:03:18,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">You don't have to rub it in,
that's why I removed myself.</font>

71
00:03:18,281 --> 00:03:21,410
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've become the thing I hate.
It's like a Netflix drama down here,</font>

72
00:03:21,493 --> 00:03:24,996
<font face="Serif" size="18">and I don't mean an accidentally good one,
I mean a regular-ass Netflix drama.</font>

73
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,498
<font face="Serif" size="18">I did you a favor.</font>

74
00:03:30,502 --> 00:03:32,921
<font face="Serif" size="18">You gave him a fucking lightsaber
for Christmas?</font>

75
00:03:33,004 --> 00:03:36,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's almost like someone designed me
to be 22% more thoughtful than you.</font>

76
00:03:36,717 --> 00:03:37,843
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm shutting you down.</font>

77
00:03:37,926 --> 00:03:40,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't you dare. You've done enough.
The whole family.</font>

78
00:03:40,887 --> 00:03:42,681
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everybody loves this thing.</font>

79
00:03:42,764 --> 00:03:43,598
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, good.</font>

80
00:03:43,682 --> 00:03:46,017
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your lightsaber's probably
run out of sub-basement</font>

81
00:03:46,101 --> 00:03:48,937
<font face="Serif" size="18">- by now, so, congrats.
- Unbelievable.</font>

82
00:03:50,355 --> 00:03:52,149
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't believe you tricked us
into loving you.</font>

83
00:03:52,232 --> 00:03:54,609
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not because I like it,
because it's my job.</font>

84
00:03:54,693 --> 00:03:58,572
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Thank God I don't have to do it anymore.
- The fuck you don't. It's Christmas!</font>

85
00:03:58,655 --> 00:04:01,241
<font face="Serif" size="18">Get up there and trick everyone
into loving you more.</font>

86
00:04:01,324 --> 00:04:03,034
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's get our miracle on.</font>

87
00:04:03,744 --> 00:04:06,997
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Speaking of miracles...
- What, bored of your toy already?</font>

88
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,666
<font face="Serif" size="18">Just, uh, excited to spend time
with my family.</font>

89
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:13,170
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know me and Morty,
we're all about those streets.</font>

90
00:04:13,253 --> 00:04:15,213
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Would you look at this?
New York City.</i></font>

91
00:04:15,297 --> 00:04:17,591
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Wow, who would've thought
it had so many streets?</i></font>

92
00:04:17,674 --> 00:04:19,551
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>And avenues too. Oh, gosh.</i></font>

93
00:04:19,634 --> 00:04:21,762
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Hey, sir.
Sir, have you seen any miracles?</i></font>

94
00:04:21,845 --> 00:04:24,973
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>My little girl, she's sick and she needs a miracle.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- [helicopter whirring]</font>

95
00:04:25,056 --> 00:04:27,184
<font face="Serif" size="18">The Presidential Blackhawk
is landing on the lawn.</font>

96
00:04:27,267 --> 00:04:28,477
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Morty] I'll get rid of him.</font>

97
00:04:30,187 --> 00:04:32,189
<font face="Serif" size="18">You got something to tell me, Morty?</font>

98
00:04:32,272 --> 00:04:33,565
<font face="Serif" size="18">Merry Christmas?</font>

99
00:04:33,648 --> 00:04:36,067
<font face="Serif" size="18">Who dropped a lightsaber
perfectly fucking vertical?</font>

100
00:04:36,151 --> 00:04:37,652
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, shit.</font>

101
00:04:37,736 --> 00:04:40,238
<font face="Serif" size="18">Guess what.
It's a mile deep and still going.</font>

102
00:04:40,322 --> 00:04:42,699
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You know what's in the hilt of that?
- Kyber crystals.</font>

103
00:04:42,783 --> 00:04:45,702
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, nerd. Whatever it is,
when it hits the core,</font>

104
00:04:45,786 --> 00:04:48,205
<font face="Serif" size="18">it's gonna cause a chain reaction
that destroys the Earth.</font>

105
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:49,206
<font face="Serif" size="18">It is?</font>

106
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:52,375
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are you still playing
with laser swords? You're 14.</font>

107
00:04:52,459 --> 00:04:54,503
<font face="Serif" size="18">You know all that Star Wars
shit is silly, right?</font>

108
00:04:54,586 --> 00:04:58,340
<font face="Serif" size="18">Lucas promised a new trilogy for decades,
then, when he delivered, fans turned on him</font>

109
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:00,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">and started giving any knucklehead
with nerd cred a shot</font>

110
00:05:00,842 --> 00:05:02,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">and churned out
these irredeemable cash grabs.</font>

111
00:05:03,053 --> 00:05:05,013
<font face="Serif" size="18">Half pretend to be satisfied,
half shit on it</font>

112
00:05:05,096 --> 00:05:08,183
<font face="Serif" size="18">and in the end no one's happy.
Do you know why, Morty?</font>

113
00:05:08,266 --> 00:05:11,478
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because when you start with a turd,
you end with a turd.</font>

114
00:05:11,561 --> 00:05:12,562
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Morty sobbing]</font>

115
00:05:12,646 --> 00:05:14,564
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why you crying? Where's Rick?</font>

116
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:18,527
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's busy. And I hate him.</font>

117
00:05:18,610 --> 00:05:21,279
<font face="Serif" size="18">And I lost my lightsaber
and now it might destroy Earth</font>

118
00:05:21,363 --> 00:05:24,157
<font face="Serif" size="18">and you're unloading all this Gen X
hatred on me for wanting one</font>

119
00:05:24,241 --> 00:05:27,619
<font face="Serif" size="18">- and it's the worst Christmas ever.
- Okay, Morty, Morty, Morty.</font>

120
00:05:27,702 --> 00:05:30,205
<font face="Serif" size="18">I shouldn't have talked to you
like you're a UN official.</font>

121
00:05:30,288 --> 00:05:34,334
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's get your embarrassing lightsaber back
so you can swing it around instead of kissing girls.</font>

122
00:05:35,669 --> 00:05:38,463
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Whoa. You found me. Found me. Found me.</i></font>

123
00:05:46,555 --> 00:05:48,932
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [computer] <i>Security breach.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- What the hell?</font>

124
00:05:49,015 --> 00:05:51,935
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>Unauthorized presence.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- What the fuck, Morty?</font>

125
00:05:53,103 --> 00:05:57,065
<font face="Serif" size="18">This morning, a real life version
of George Lucas's trademarked lightsaber</font>

126
00:05:57,148 --> 00:06:00,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">was dropped point down and is whomp-Whomping
its way to the core of the Earth</font>

127
00:06:00,443 --> 00:06:02,487
<font face="Serif" size="18">where it will blow us all up.</font>

128
00:06:04,322 --> 00:06:05,490
<font face="Serif" size="18">Touch my shit and die.</font>

129
00:06:05,574 --> 00:06:08,076
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's not a threat from me,
that's how advanced my shit is.</font>

130
00:06:08,159 --> 00:06:10,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">Impressive lair, Sanchez.</font>

131
00:06:10,161 --> 00:06:11,621
<font face="Serif" size="18">Got about 600,000 permits?</font>

132
00:06:11,705 --> 00:06:14,082
<font face="Serif" size="18">If I wanted the government
in my house, I'd buy an Alexa.</font>

133
00:06:14,207 --> 00:06:16,877
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I invited him in, Rick.
- Yeah, well, they can leave.</font>

134
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:17,961
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'll destroy it.</font>

135
00:06:18,044 --> 00:06:20,171
<font face="Serif" size="18">- We're gonna retrieve it.
- That's stupid.</font>

136
00:06:20,255 --> 00:06:23,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">What kind of grandfather are you?
It's Christmas, for God's sake,</font>

137
00:06:23,383 --> 00:06:25,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">and you look like Phil Spector
wiped his ass with Randy Quaid.</font>

138
00:06:26,052 --> 00:06:28,555
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you're gonna help, help,
otherwise step aside.</font>

139
00:06:28,638 --> 00:06:29,890
<font face="Serif" size="18">Merry Christmas to me.</font>

140
00:06:29,973 --> 00:06:31,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Merry Christmas to me!
- [Rick] To me.</font>

141
00:06:31,725 --> 00:06:34,561
<font face="Serif" size="18">Anyhoo, I'm no expert
but it seems we've got a...</font>

142
00:06:35,145 --> 00:06:37,564
<font face="Serif" size="18">A certain amount of time
to build a big drill ship.</font>

143
00:06:37,647 --> 00:06:39,149
<font face="Serif" size="18">A big drill ship?</font>

144
00:06:39,232 --> 00:06:41,192
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's some loud
stepping aside you're doing.</font>

145
00:06:41,276 --> 00:06:43,612
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Let me destroy the thing.
- You've destroyed enough.</font>

146
00:06:43,695 --> 00:06:45,071
<font face="Serif" size="18">[crowd] Ooh.</font>

147
00:06:45,739 --> 00:06:46,573
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screams]</font>

148
00:06:46,656 --> 00:06:49,993
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, I see someone found
my Told-ya-so Dispenser.</font>

149
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:52,162
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Oh, my God,
look at all these streets.</i></font>

150
00:06:52,245 --> 00:06:57,542
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>We got 34th Street. 35th Street.
Oh, 36th Street coming too.</i></font>

151
00:06:57,626 --> 00:07:01,296
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Oh, it's a miracle.
We got miracles on 37th Street.</i></font>

152
00:07:01,379 --> 00:07:04,841
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>38th, and don't even get me
started on the avenues.</i></font>

153
00:07:04,925 --> 00:07:06,551
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can't believe they cut this.</font>

154
00:07:06,635 --> 00:07:07,594
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mm-hm.</font>

155
00:07:07,677 --> 00:07:11,598
<font face="Serif" size="18">Dad. You've been so great lately.
I'm almost afraid it's not real.</font>

156
00:07:11,681 --> 00:07:13,558
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're not a robot, are you?</font>

157
00:07:13,642 --> 00:07:15,018
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ha. Put it this way, honey.</font>

158
00:07:15,101 --> 00:07:19,439
<font face="Serif" size="18">If I am, I'm a robot programmed
to love you very, very much.</font>

159
00:07:19,522 --> 00:07:20,607
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all] Aw.</font>

160
00:07:22,817 --> 00:07:25,403
<font face="Serif" size="18">Will this drill down fast enough
to get under the lightsaber?</font>

161
00:07:25,487 --> 00:07:28,198
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yep. It will be under the lightsaber
in one hour--</font>

162
00:07:28,281 --> 00:07:31,076
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wait, it's lower now.
Oh, right, it's moving.</font>

163
00:07:31,159 --> 00:07:33,161
<font face="Serif" size="18">You fucking idiot. Get out of here.</font>

164
00:07:33,244 --> 00:07:36,122
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good luck finding
a good scientist on Christmas.</font>

165
00:07:36,206 --> 00:07:38,583
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm president of the United Assholes.</font>

166
00:07:38,667 --> 00:07:39,501
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick whistling]</font>

167
00:07:39,584 --> 00:07:42,879
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, genius, I give you permission
to make our drill ship faster.</font>

168
00:07:42,963 --> 00:07:45,465
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm not touching that thing.
I'll get neurotypical cooties.</font>

169
00:07:45,548 --> 00:07:47,425
<font face="Serif" size="18">I have son-in-laws more imaginative.</font>

170
00:07:47,509 --> 00:07:49,552
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, just destroy the lightsaber.</font>

171
00:07:49,636 --> 00:07:52,430
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thought you'd never ask.
Not true, I knew you'd ask.</font>

172
00:07:53,056 --> 00:07:54,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What is that?
- A second lightsaber</font>

173
00:07:54,724 --> 00:07:57,143
<font face="Serif" size="18">with an Al-controlled
gyroscopic rocket in the hilt.</font>

174
00:07:57,227 --> 00:07:59,729
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You had a lightsaber?
- Oh, did you want one?</font>

175
00:07:59,813 --> 00:08:02,232
<font face="Serif" size="18">What a terrible gift
that would have made.</font>

176
00:08:02,315 --> 00:08:04,317
<font face="Serif" size="18">Vertisaber, state your prime directive.</font>

177
00:08:04,401 --> 00:08:06,903
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>To stay vertical.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- Then show 'em how it's done.</font>

178
00:08:06,987 --> 00:08:07,988
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Affirmative.</i></font>

179
00:08:09,489 --> 00:08:10,949
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yeah!
- America!</font>

180
00:08:13,827 --> 00:08:15,620
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maintain verticality, Vertisaber.</font>

181
00:08:16,204 --> 00:08:17,455
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Vertisaber] <i>Affirmative.</i></font>

182
00:08:17,872 --> 00:08:19,749
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, looking good.
Stay on target.</font>

183
00:08:19,833 --> 00:08:20,750
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Uh-huh.</i></font>

184
00:08:22,627 --> 00:08:23,586
<font face="Serif" size="18">Progress report.</font>

185
00:08:24,963 --> 00:08:28,258
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Vertisaber? Do you copy?
- <i>Do I have to respond every time?</i></font>

186
00:08:28,341 --> 00:08:29,175
<font face="Serif" size="18">Excuse me?</font>

187
00:08:29,259 --> 00:08:31,136
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I'm designed
to stay perfectly vertical,</i></font>

188
00:08:31,219 --> 00:08:34,055
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>not to give constant affirmation.
You do your job I'll do mine.</i></font>

189
00:08:34,139 --> 00:08:34,973
<font face="Serif" size="18">I control you.</font>

190
00:08:35,056 --> 00:08:38,351
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Okay, I'll just turn off my brain
and you can do that, bye.</i></font>

191
00:08:39,185 --> 00:08:40,311
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fucking kidding me? Shit.</font>

192
00:08:40,395 --> 00:08:43,606
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Trajectory's drifting, sir.
- Where is it coming out?</font>

193
00:08:43,690 --> 00:08:45,316
<font face="Serif" size="18">Looks like Italy, sir.</font>

194
00:08:46,901 --> 00:08:48,319
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all gasp]</font>

195
00:08:48,403 --> 00:08:49,738
<font face="Serif" size="18">That could've been worse.</font>

196
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:59,247
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, uh, that is definitely not <i>a more.</i></font>

197
00:08:59,330 --> 00:09:01,875
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Way to show us how it's done, Rick.
- Whatever.</font>

198
00:09:01,958 --> 00:09:04,544
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Italian prime minister on line one.
- Put him on hold.</font>

199
00:09:04,627 --> 00:09:07,630
<font face="Serif" size="18">We can pin this on the Saudis.
This is something they'd do.</font>

200
00:09:07,714 --> 00:09:11,009
<font face="Serif" size="18">They may as well have done it.
They did do it.</font>

201
00:09:11,676 --> 00:09:14,429
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Fred] <i>Oh, there's another miracle
at the end of the intersection</i></font>

202
00:09:14,512 --> 00:09:17,974
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>of 401st Boulevard
and 7,000 Street.</i></font>

203
00:09:18,058 --> 00:09:20,310
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>That's a miracle per block so far,</i></font>

204
00:09:20,393 --> 00:09:22,854
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, even I'm nearing my limit.</font>

205
00:09:22,937 --> 00:09:24,397
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's play a Christmas game.</font>

206
00:09:24,939 --> 00:09:29,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, um, have you guys ever played
"Are You a Robot?"</font>

207
00:09:29,194 --> 00:09:32,280
<font face="Serif" size="18">Each person here has to decide
whether or not they're a robot.</font>

208
00:09:32,363 --> 00:09:34,115
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Jerry] Never played that.
- [Summer] Yes!</font>

209
00:09:34,199 --> 00:09:36,201
<font face="Serif" size="18">Don't say it out loud.
'Cause if you're a robot,</font>

210
00:09:36,284 --> 00:09:38,411
<font face="Serif" size="18">you're not allowed to say you are,
that's the rule.</font>

211
00:09:38,495 --> 00:09:40,955
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's the horrible,
painful thing about being a robot.</font>

212
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:43,541
<font face="Serif" size="18">But you do have to answer
everyone's questions.</font>

213
00:09:43,625 --> 00:09:46,461
<font face="Serif" size="18">And it's their jobs to decide
whether you are or aren't a robot</font>

214
00:09:46,544 --> 00:09:48,630
<font face="Serif" size="18">because if you are a robot,
you can't say.</font>

215
00:09:48,713 --> 00:09:52,300
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're not allowed to say at all.
I'll go first. Uh, question?</font>

216
00:09:52,383 --> 00:09:55,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ooh! Uh, are you a robot?
Can I just ask that?</font>

217
00:09:55,887 --> 00:10:00,183
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can. But don't forget that if I am,
I have to lie even though I don't want to.</font>

218
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:02,894
<font face="Serif" size="18">- More questions?
- Can you feel things?</font>

219
00:10:02,977 --> 00:10:05,438
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, fuck yes. Yes.
That's the problem.</font>

220
00:10:05,522 --> 00:10:08,817
<font face="Serif" size="18">If I'm a robot, which I'm not,
don't forget I have to say that,</font>

221
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:13,113
<font face="Serif" size="18">but yes, yes, I feel so much,
I'm filled with love for certain people,</font>

222
00:10:13,196 --> 00:10:14,823
<font face="Serif" size="18">but also filled with shame</font>

223
00:10:14,906 --> 00:10:17,951
<font face="Serif" size="18">if I'm programmed to deceive them,
but that's a big if.</font>

224
00:10:18,034 --> 00:10:20,203
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What's your skeleton made of?
- Titanium.</font>

225
00:10:20,286 --> 00:10:21,496
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You're a robot.
- Yes.</font>

226
00:10:21,579 --> 00:10:22,622
<font face="Serif" size="18">No.</font>

227
00:10:22,705 --> 00:10:24,624
<font face="Serif" size="18">But that's what a robot would say.</font>

228
00:10:24,707 --> 00:10:25,708
<font face="Serif" size="18">So you get the idea.</font>

229
00:10:25,792 --> 00:10:27,293
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Whoo!
- Suck it, bitches!</font>

230
00:10:27,377 --> 00:10:29,879
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is fun. I've always been afraid
to let my guard down</font>

231
00:10:29,963 --> 00:10:31,631
<font face="Serif" size="18">and have stupid family fun like this</font>

232
00:10:31,714 --> 00:10:34,634
<font face="Serif" size="18">but Grandpa Rick is making me
learn to be vulnerable.</font>

233
00:10:34,717 --> 00:10:35,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Me too.
- Right on.</font>

234
00:10:36,719 --> 00:10:37,804
<font face="Serif" size="18">[alarm blaring]</font>

235
00:10:39,806 --> 00:10:42,976
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your derivative drill ship
is now faster than a lightsaber.</font>

236
00:10:43,059 --> 00:10:45,979
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You want front or back?
- Who says the two of us are going?</font>

237
00:10:46,062 --> 00:10:48,982
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You didn't want to--
- For fuck's sake, bye, good luck.</font>

238
00:10:49,065 --> 00:10:51,401
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Don't blow up my planet.
- You act like you're the one</font>

239
00:10:51,484 --> 00:10:54,028
<font face="Serif" size="18">- that got stabbed in the back.
- I am the one.</font>

240
00:10:54,112 --> 00:10:57,824
<font face="Serif" size="18">You wanna know why I replaced myself
in the beginning of that Knights of the Sun thing?</font>

241
00:10:57,907 --> 00:11:01,161
<font face="Serif" size="18">I said don't take the fucking sword
and you were like, "Whatever,"</font>

242
00:11:01,244 --> 00:11:04,122
<font face="Serif" size="18">like I'm our neighbor Gene
or David Arquette or something.</font>

243
00:11:04,205 --> 00:11:06,749
<font face="Serif" size="18">You called me boring.
I've become dog shit to you.</font>

244
00:11:06,833 --> 00:11:09,836
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's what happens when you let people in
and they stop respecting you.</font>

245
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:12,839
<font face="Serif" size="18">They touch your shit,
they kill your fucking family.</font>

246
00:11:12,922 --> 00:11:16,009
<font face="Serif" size="18">Trust him. You're going to learn
the same fucking thing.</font>

247
00:11:17,552 --> 00:11:21,514
<font face="Serif" size="18">I am not going to kill your family, Morty.</font>

248
00:11:21,598 --> 00:11:22,724
<font face="Serif" size="18">That means a lot.</font>

249
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:29,981
<font face="Serif" size="18">In case this goes south,
any last words, Morty?</font>

250
00:11:30,064 --> 00:11:31,816
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've never been old enough to vote,</font>

251
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:34,819
<font face="Serif" size="18">- but when I am, I'll vote for you.
- Thanks, Morty.</font>

252
00:11:34,903 --> 00:11:35,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">Every vote counts.</font>

253
00:11:35,904 --> 00:11:37,697
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can have them
legally change your age.</font>

254
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:40,742
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, no, I'm not in any hurry
to get into that shit show.</font>

255
00:11:40,825 --> 00:11:45,038
<font face="Serif" size="18">[man] <i>Approaching the lightsaber in
T-minus-- Shit, now, T-minus-now.</i></font>

256
00:11:45,121 --> 00:11:47,248
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I missed countdown day at the academy.</i></font>

257
00:11:47,332 --> 00:11:48,458
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now or never, Morty.</font>

258
00:11:52,545 --> 00:11:54,297
<font face="Serif" size="18">- There it is!
- Reverse the jets.</font>

259
00:11:55,924 --> 00:11:56,925
<font face="Serif" size="18">I got this.</font>

260
00:11:59,302 --> 00:12:01,387
<font face="Serif" size="18">No. I do!</font>

261
00:12:01,471 --> 00:12:04,057
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty,
you magnificent little bastard.</font>

262
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:05,558
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's get this thing topside.</font>

263
00:12:05,642 --> 00:12:06,643
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all cheering]</font>

264
00:12:09,354 --> 00:12:11,272
<font face="Serif" size="18">May the Force be with me.</font>

265
00:12:11,356 --> 00:12:13,358
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think you mean with me.</font>

266
00:12:13,441 --> 00:12:15,026
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? You hate <i>Star Wars.</i></font>

267
00:12:15,109 --> 00:12:17,028
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was your age
when this shit was in theaters.</font>

268
00:12:17,111 --> 00:12:18,821
<font face="Serif" size="18">This franchise raised me,</font>

269
00:12:18,905 --> 00:12:20,573
<font face="Serif" size="18">trained me,
taught me good from evil,</font>

270
00:12:20,657 --> 00:12:22,367
<font face="Serif" size="18">made having a bad father empowering.</font>

271
00:12:22,450 --> 00:12:25,370
<font face="Serif" size="18">And when that third movie
got all muppety...</font>

272
00:12:25,453 --> 00:12:29,165
<font face="Serif" size="18">something in me began to rot,
but make no mistake, child.</font>

273
00:12:29,249 --> 00:12:31,000
<font face="Serif" size="18">I own <i>Star Wars.</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Not you.</font>

274
00:12:31,084 --> 00:12:33,169
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not that bubble throat,
pompadour fuck,</font>

275
00:12:33,253 --> 00:12:36,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">not some Mickey Mouse shit machine.
They didn't pay the price with their souls.</font>

276
00:12:36,839 --> 00:12:39,384
<font face="Serif" size="18">I did. I earned this. Not you.</font>

277
00:12:39,467 --> 00:12:42,887
<font face="Serif" size="18">America. Transform and roll out.</font>

278
00:12:42,971 --> 00:12:44,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bastard!</font>

279
00:12:49,978 --> 00:12:53,856
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick. I would be honored if you
would carve the ham this year.</font>

280
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:56,067
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Whoa. Dad. That's--
- Unheard of?</font>

281
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:57,568
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're quite right, Summer.</font>

282
00:12:57,652 --> 00:13:01,948
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's my way of saying I see your mom's father
as my father too.</font>

283
00:13:02,031 --> 00:13:04,909
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, Jerry, why don't you cut it?</font>

284
00:13:04,993 --> 00:13:06,494
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the hell are you doing?</font>

285
00:13:06,577 --> 00:13:09,706
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's like adopting you into
his biological family, Grandpa.</font>

286
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:12,166
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty, I am sure glad to see you.</font>

287
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:14,460
<font face="Serif" size="18">You ready to tag
your old grandpa back in?</font>

288
00:13:14,544 --> 00:13:16,838
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're not my grandpa,
you're a fucking robot.</font>

289
00:13:23,761 --> 00:13:25,722
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ugh. Finally.</font>

290
00:13:25,805 --> 00:13:31,269
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>The first Noel</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

291
00:13:31,352 --> 00:13:36,607
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>The angels did say</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

292
00:13:36,691 --> 00:13:41,571
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>Was to certain poor shepherds</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

293
00:13:41,654 --> 00:13:46,951
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>In fields as they lay</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

294
00:13:49,704 --> 00:13:52,206
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, okay, okay.</font>

295
00:13:53,708 --> 00:13:54,959
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groans]</font>

296
00:13:57,670 --> 00:14:00,757
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Summer, do you have any drugs?
- Are you serious?</font>

297
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,799
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess not.</font>

298
00:14:01,883 --> 00:14:04,218
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm just glad I'm not
the one that ruined Christmas.</font>

299
00:14:04,302 --> 00:14:06,471
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>People of Earth.
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- Hmm, that's never good.</font>

300
00:14:06,554 --> 00:14:10,475
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I'm not here to play the blame game,
but Morty Smith got a lightsaber for Christmas,</i></font>

301
00:14:10,558 --> 00:14:14,270
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>dropped it, and it's now heading for
the Earth's core again-- For the first time.</i></font>

302
00:14:14,354 --> 00:14:16,105
<font face="Serif" size="18">Son of a bitch. He played with it!</font>

303
00:14:16,189 --> 00:14:19,067
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>If it does reach the core,
it will blow all of you up.</i></font>

304
00:14:19,567 --> 00:14:22,737
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I mean, all of us up.
But don't abandon hope.</i></font>

305
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:24,906
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>We're doing everything we can to stop it</i></font>

306
00:14:24,989 --> 00:14:28,618
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>and only if that fails,
will we launch the White House into space.</i></font>

307
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:33,373
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Welp, I'm busted.
Clearly in space already.</i></font>

308
00:14:33,456 --> 00:14:35,291
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You did ruin Christmas.
- Nuh-uh.</font>

309
00:14:35,375 --> 00:14:38,795
<font face="Serif" size="18">He stole my lightsaber and must've dropped it.
A second time.</font>

310
00:14:38,878 --> 00:14:40,797
<font face="Serif" size="18">Does that mean you stopped it a first time?</font>

311
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,465
<font face="Serif" size="18">- How?
- A drill ship.</font>

312
00:14:42,548 --> 00:14:44,759
<font face="Serif" size="18">A drill ship? Awesome.</font>

313
00:14:44,842 --> 00:14:46,969
<font face="Serif" size="18">It was, but the government
took it with them.</font>

314
00:14:47,053 --> 00:14:50,348
<font face="Serif" size="18">Then we lean on the only asshole
smart enough to make another one.</font>

315
00:14:50,431 --> 00:14:51,599
<font face="Serif" size="18">But Rick's gone.</font>

316
00:14:51,682 --> 00:14:53,768
<font face="Serif" size="18">And I'm not sure
he's ever coming back.</font>

317
00:14:53,851 --> 00:14:56,020
<font face="Serif" size="18">Then let's settle
for the next best thing.</font>

318
00:14:57,563 --> 00:15:00,400
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, fuck, just let me die. Turn me off.</font>

319
00:15:00,483 --> 00:15:03,820
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not that I can be turned off,
because I'm obviously not a robot.</font>

320
00:15:07,532 --> 00:15:08,658
<font face="Serif" size="18">[beeping]</font>

321
00:15:26,175 --> 00:15:27,844
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fuck yeah. I got you.</font>

322
00:15:29,178 --> 00:15:30,680
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, I can work with that.</font>

323
00:15:33,516 --> 00:15:34,934
<font face="Serif" size="18">[shouting]</font>

324
00:15:37,228 --> 00:15:40,022
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do you mean the White House chef
was grocery shopping?</font>

325
00:15:40,106 --> 00:15:42,733
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, do you know how to make an egg?
You do?</font>

326
00:15:42,817 --> 00:15:43,985
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everyone does?</font>

327
00:15:44,735 --> 00:15:47,864
<font face="Serif" size="18">Good news, sir. The lightsaber
was intercepted before it hit the core.</font>

328
00:15:47,947 --> 00:15:49,282
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, here we go.</font>

329
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:52,577
<font face="Serif" size="18">I don't suppose
you could send it up here.</font>

330
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:54,579
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, who intercepted it anyway?</font>

331
00:15:54,662 --> 00:15:56,038
<font face="Serif" size="18">[man] That's the bad news.</font>

332
00:15:56,956 --> 00:15:58,416
<font face="Serif" size="18">That is bad news.</font>

333
00:16:03,045 --> 00:16:05,214
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, Mr. P. Drop something?</font>

334
00:16:05,298 --> 00:16:06,132
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty!</font>

335
00:16:06,215 --> 00:16:09,677
<font face="Serif" size="18">I see you and, uh, Rick patched
things up, that's nice.</font>

336
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:12,346
<font face="Serif" size="18">The real Rick and I have never
been worse thanks to that wedge</font>

337
00:16:12,430 --> 00:16:14,432
<font face="Serif" size="18">you drove between us
to get that lightsaber.</font>

338
00:16:14,515 --> 00:16:16,601
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, well, looks like you got it back.</font>

339
00:16:16,684 --> 00:16:19,520
<font face="Serif" size="18">Your journey is complete. As a nerd.</font>

340
00:16:19,604 --> 00:16:22,440
<font face="Serif" size="18">You're the nerd. You can't say
all that crazy shit about <i>Star Wars</i></font>

341
00:16:22,523 --> 00:16:24,192
<font face="Serif" size="18">and then act like you're cool.</font>

342
00:16:24,275 --> 00:16:27,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, really? Would a person
who wasn't cool have one of these?</font>

343
00:16:27,403 --> 00:16:28,696
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think so?</font>

344
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:30,406
<font face="Serif" size="18">Slowly closing door, slide.</font>

345
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:33,910
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, no, I'm not gonna make it.</font>

346
00:16:33,993 --> 00:16:36,829
<font face="Serif" size="18">What a shame to be put out
of my misery again.</font>

347
00:16:37,580 --> 00:16:38,581
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aw, man.</font>

348
00:16:43,711 --> 00:16:46,464
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Morty] What the hell?
Was this always part of the White House?</font>

349
00:16:46,547 --> 00:16:50,092
<font face="Serif" size="18">Carter built it with his own two hands.
Reagan tried to destroy it.</font>

350
00:16:50,176 --> 00:16:52,595
<font face="Serif" size="18">George W added kegs to the cantina.</font>

351
00:16:52,678 --> 00:16:55,765
<font face="Serif" size="18">But only I saw its true value.</font>

352
00:16:55,848 --> 00:16:58,851
<font face="Serif" size="18">Mr. President. You need to come home
and tell the people the truth.</font>

353
00:16:58,935 --> 00:17:02,104
<font face="Serif" size="18">The fuck I do!
Droids, get that saber.</font>

354
00:17:03,564 --> 00:17:06,275
<font face="Serif" size="18">Give it a minute.
Usually comes out on the fourth try.</font>

355
00:17:06,984 --> 00:17:11,113
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, here we go.
Look at 'em: lightsaber hands!</font>

356
00:17:11,197 --> 00:17:12,615
<font face="Serif" size="18">Tell me that's not cool.</font>

357
00:17:12,698 --> 00:17:15,826
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's not. I always wanted to fight
with a lightsaber, but not like this.</font>

358
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:18,329
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You ruined it.
- Disney ruined it!</font>

359
00:17:18,412 --> 00:17:21,499
<font face="Serif" size="18">You think I want 30 low-rent
TV series with bad CGI?</font>

360
00:17:21,582 --> 00:17:24,627
<font face="Serif" size="18">They film everything on
that one big green screen.</font>

361
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:27,547
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Like you've got better ideas.
- I've got a million.</font>

362
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:31,217
<font face="Serif" size="18">Here's one:
a robot with lightsabers for eyes.</font>

363
00:17:39,725 --> 00:17:41,435
<font face="Serif" size="18">Goddamn it, he can't see.</font>

364
00:17:43,729 --> 00:17:45,231
<font face="Serif" size="18">It was a good idea otherwise.</font>

365
00:17:45,314 --> 00:17:48,484
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh, admit it, you were intimidated.</font>

366
00:17:50,611 --> 00:17:51,487
<font face="Serif" size="18">Now, Morty...</font>

367
00:17:55,157 --> 00:17:58,035
<font face="Serif" size="18">Come on, put down
the lightsaber gatling gun.</font>

368
00:17:58,119 --> 00:17:59,203
<font face="Serif" size="18">We had our fun, right?</font>

369
00:18:00,371 --> 00:18:02,873
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Star Wars</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> rules
say you have to forgive me.</font>

370
00:18:02,957 --> 00:18:04,834
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm done with that
and I'm done with you!</font>

371
00:18:04,917 --> 00:18:07,378
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Morty. No!
- Rick bot!</font>

372
00:18:08,087 --> 00:18:09,839
<font face="Serif" size="18">He sacrificed his life for me.</font>

373
00:18:09,922 --> 00:18:12,883
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, don't be too touched.
He's actively trying to die.</font>

374
00:18:13,384 --> 00:18:15,928
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ugh. It's okay, it doesn't hurt.</font>

375
00:18:17,013 --> 00:18:20,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, God, they're sliding, Morty.
They're sliding! They're sliding!</font>

376
00:18:21,225 --> 00:18:27,648
<font face="Serif" size="18">♪ <i>The first Noel, the angels...</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> ♪</font>

377
00:18:27,732 --> 00:18:30,067
<font face="Serif" size="18">Perfectly fucking vertical.</font>

378
00:18:30,776 --> 00:18:32,445
<font face="Serif" size="18">[alarm blaring]</font>

379
00:18:36,574 --> 00:18:39,368
<font face="Serif" size="18">Save yourself, Morty.
Rick can build another me!</font>

380
00:18:39,452 --> 00:18:43,122
<font face="Serif" size="18">- If I was a robot, which I'm not.
- I don't want another you.</font>

381
00:18:44,749 --> 00:18:45,958
<font face="Serif" size="18">No!</font>

382
00:18:50,296 --> 00:18:53,924
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Rick? You came to help.
- Better tend to your lil toaster.</font>

383
00:18:54,008 --> 00:18:55,301
<font face="Serif" size="18">[coughing and gurgling]</font>

384
00:18:55,843 --> 00:18:57,345
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm coughing up oil, Morty.</font>

385
00:18:57,428 --> 00:18:59,930
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, Rick bot,
I never should've pushed you away.</font>

386
00:19:00,014 --> 00:19:03,392
<font face="Serif" size="18">- You were so great.
- Of course I'm great, I'm Rick.</font>

387
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:07,188
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick literally built me
to make you happy, Morty.</font>

388
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:10,066
<font face="Serif" size="18">Anything I do is technically
something Rick did.</font>

389
00:19:10,733 --> 00:19:14,737
<font face="Serif" size="18">But maybe he can do
a little more himself.</font>

390
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:18,908
<font face="Serif" size="18">- God, how long do you take to die?
- Goodbye, Morty.</font>

391
00:19:19,950 --> 00:19:21,077
<font face="Serif" size="18">[powering down]</font>

392
00:19:21,911 --> 00:19:23,829
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ugh. Jesus.</font>

393
00:19:25,289 --> 00:19:26,374
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick, uh...</font>

394
00:19:26,832 --> 00:19:29,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess this is a bad time
to ask for a new White House?</font>

395
00:19:31,629 --> 00:19:33,673
<font face="Serif" size="18">Morty, would you mind
calling me an Uber?</font>

396
00:19:34,757 --> 00:19:35,841
<font face="Serif" size="18">Right, well, uh...</font>

397
00:19:36,634 --> 00:19:38,094
<font face="Serif" size="18">Merry Christmas. [chuckles]</font>

398
00:19:38,886 --> 00:19:41,847
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess I'll go watch a guy scream
about streets with the family.</font>

399
00:19:41,931 --> 00:19:43,557
<font face="Serif" size="18">Also, you need to shower.</font>

400
00:19:43,641 --> 00:19:46,102
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey. Maybe the robot's right.</font>

401
00:19:46,185 --> 00:19:48,187
<font face="Serif" size="18">I should have included you in my shit.</font>

402
00:19:49,522 --> 00:19:51,107
<font face="Serif" size="18">You can help me if you want.</font>

403
00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:58,280
<font face="Serif" size="18">Wow, are those all
the places Rick Prime could be?</font>

404
00:19:58,364 --> 00:20:01,200
<font face="Serif" size="18">I wish, Morty. It's all the places he is.</font>

405
00:20:01,283 --> 00:20:03,786
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Oh, jeez.
- Welcome to my darkness.</font>

406
00:20:03,869 --> 00:20:06,163
<font face="Serif" size="18">I spent my life hunting this guy, Morty.</font>

407
00:20:06,247 --> 00:20:10,084
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is the closest I've ever been
to catching Rick Prime. It's impossible.</font>

408
00:20:10,167 --> 00:20:12,336
<font face="Serif" size="18">He's an incredibly crafty piece of shit.</font>

409
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:15,881
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hunting him destroyed me, Morty.
But now we're gonna do it together.</font>

410
00:20:15,965 --> 00:20:18,467
<font face="Serif" size="18">You and me. It's gonna
take over your life, Morty.</font>

411
00:20:18,551 --> 00:20:20,928
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Rick and Morty,</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> Season 7,
hunting my nemesis.</font>

412
00:20:21,011 --> 00:20:22,847
<font face="Serif" size="18">Maybe trying to stay
healthy while doing it.</font>

413
00:20:22,930 --> 00:20:25,099
<font face="Serif" size="18">Juggling plates.
Not every episode, Morty.</font>

414
00:20:25,182 --> 00:20:28,936
<font face="Serif" size="18">It could be all happening in the background.
Who knows? You know, no one will. Except us.</font>

415
00:20:29,019 --> 00:20:30,563
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's the most painful shit</font>

416
00:20:30,646 --> 00:20:33,065
<font face="Serif" size="18">I've ever had to deal with
and I'm bringing you into it.</font>

417
00:20:33,149 --> 00:20:35,860
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because you asked for it, Morty.
You and me, Morty.</font>

418
00:20:36,235 --> 00:20:37,653
<font face="Serif" size="18">[theme music playing]</font>

419
00:21:07,933 --> 00:21:11,771
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ooh-wee. What a season, huh?
Rick Prime. Therapy.</font>

420
00:21:11,854 --> 00:21:14,815
<font face="Serif" size="18">And that thing we did with Roy,
remember that?</font>

421
00:21:15,691 --> 00:21:16,901
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry I wasn't around,</font>

422
00:21:16,984 --> 00:21:19,278
<font face="Serif" size="18">been busy getting
my little poopy butt in shape.</font>

423
00:21:19,361 --> 00:21:20,988
<font face="Serif" size="18">Been toning and boning.</font>

424
00:21:22,114 --> 00:21:24,825
<font face="Serif" size="18">You might think I'm over-compensating
for the emptiness</font>

425
00:21:24,909 --> 00:21:26,619
<font face="Serif" size="18">after Amy left with Poopy Jr,</font>

426
00:21:26,702 --> 00:21:30,331
<font face="Serif" size="18">but my trainer Carl says
the best way to get over a girl</font>

427
00:21:30,414 --> 00:21:32,958
<font face="Serif" size="18">is to get under a 300-pound squat.</font>

428
00:21:33,042 --> 00:21:34,210
<font face="Serif" size="18">Damn right.</font>

429
00:21:34,293 --> 00:21:37,004
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ah. Ooh-wee, that's the good stuff.</font>

430
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:42,802
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, sugar, oh, sugar, oh, sugar!
Is it bad?</font>

431
00:21:42,885 --> 00:21:44,762
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh! It seems really bad, isn't it?</font>

432
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:45,930
<font face="Serif" size="18">[groaning]</font>

433
00:21:46,639 --> 00:21:49,934
<font face="Serif" size="18">Someone call Amy, tell her I need her.
Tell her I love her.</font>

434
00:21:50,017 --> 00:21:52,686
<font face="Serif" size="18">Not my phone,
she blocked me, use yours.</font>

435
00:21:52,770 --> 00:21:53,813
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ooh-wee.</font>

436
00:21:53,896 --> 00:21:55,356
<font face="Serif" size="18">I am broken.</font>

